{
  "macro_id": "plumbing.drainSlope",
  "domain": "plumbing",
  "name": "drainSlope",
  "inputs": {
    "pipeSizeInches": {
      "type": "number"
    },
    "lengthFeet": {
      "type": "number"
    }
  },
  "reads_artifact_data": true,
  "invariants": [
    "typeof output === 'object' && output !== null",
    "typeof output.ok === 'boolean'",
    "output.ok === false || typeof output.result.pipeSize === 'string'",
    "output.ok === false || typeof output.result.length === 'string'",
    "output.ok === false || typeof output.result.slopePerFoot === 'string'",
    "output.ok === false || typeof output.result.totalDrop === 'string'",
    "output.ok === false || typeof output.result.ipcCode === 'string'",
    "output.ok === false || typeof output.result.tip === 'string'",
    "output.ok === false || Number.isFinite(parseFloat(output.result.totalDrop))",
    "output.ok === false || Number.isFinite(parseFloat(output.result.slopePerFoot))"
  ],
  "fuzz_cases": [
    {
      "input": {
        "artifact": {
          "data": {
            "pipeSizeInches": 2,
            "lengthFeet": 10
          }
        }
      },
      "expect": {
        "ok": true
      }
    },
    {
      "input": {
        "artifact": {
          "data": {
            "pipeSizeInches": 4,
            "lengthFeet": 20
          }
        }
      },
      "expect": {
        "ok": true
      }
    },
    {
      "input": {
        "artifact": {
          "data": {}
        }
      },
      "expect": {
        "ok": true
      }
    },
    {
      "input": {
        "artifact": {
          "data": {
            "pipeSizeInches": "abc",
            "lengthFeet": "Infinity"
          }
        }
      },
      "expect": {
        "ok": false
      }
    }
  ],
  "_note": "Pure compute, reads artifact.data. slopePerFoot: ≤2\"→0.25, ≤3\"→0.1875, else 0.125 \"/ft (IPC Table 704.1) ; totalDrop = round(length·slope·100)/100. Non-finite pipe size/length fall to defaults (2/10) via Number.isFinite guards — Infinity length no longer leaks an 'Infinity\"' drop (2026-06-28). PlumbCalc.tsx DrainSlopeCalculator renders pipeSize/length/slopePerFoot/totalDrop/ipcCode/tip EXACTLY (and regex-parses the leading number of totalDrop to gate the SVG cross-section) — fields verified aligned, no phantoms."
}
